 cargo. For this reason, vsl called  Falmouth UK for shortest deviation and to top up on fuel for redelivery per the TCP. This added about a day onto the voyage. We also had a bunker survey for redelivery and the cost is reflected on this voyage along with the loss for redelivery bunkers due to owners (same price both ends). The costs for redelivery total about $130,000 which were not accounted for in the generation.\n\n \n\nEU ETS estimated price of 53 euros has been placed into VMS with the estimated cost from accounting. Will be updated next week with final cost. Verified reports are attached."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-03T13:43:10.563","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Brest port costs less than estimated"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-28T18:13:25.603","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"EU ETS included with estimated cost."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-21T13:00:10.547","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"$130k of the loss is due to bunkers on redelivery. Same price both ends but the discharge ports did not have bunkers, so vsl had to deviate and take expensive fuel in UK before she could discharge."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-12T19:32:41.997","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl had to wait for tide which did not count as lay time. Deumurrage amended."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-08T14:57:43.337","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"BL qties included"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-04T21:30:20.23","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Lorient and Brest port costs included."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-04T15:40:43.94","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Updated hire rate through 10 March"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-04T15:31:36.32","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl low on bunkers and has to bunker for redelivery. Wil divert to Falmouth as there are no bunkers avail in France."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-04T14:25:45.647","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Brest and Lorient for discharge ports. Increased WS Freight. Added 2 days of demurrage."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-20T16:02:01.463","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"New Hire rate after 03 Mar 23:59. $33,000"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-14T17:10:44.463","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Bunkers barge faced delays due to weather, so ETA to LC pushed back."}],"offhireList":[{"id":197788,"dateStartUtc":null,"dateEndUtc":null,"days":null,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":null,"remark":null,"offhireBunkerList":[{"id":265981,"gradeName":"LSBF","quantity":null,"price":null,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}